snippet.title: Rezident Evil: It Is Escape
snippet.description:
https://rpgmaker.net/games/9495/

REISE is a bizarre mess that shouldn’t have been made. Starting life as the sequel to a terrible Resident Evil fan game from 2003, it gradually mutated into a Matt LeBlanc infested fever dream.
